# Доменные pipeline-ы (src/lib)

## scanner.ts — сканирование

- `walkVideoFiles` — рекурсия, skip `.*` dirs, extensions: mkv, mp4, avi, mov, webm, …
- Skip fast path: same `filePath` + `fileSize` + `fileMtime`
- Hash: `computeFileHashPrefix` — первые 16MB (`file-hash.ts`)
- Move detection: same `fileHash` + `fileSize`, different path → update path in place
- Priority: `existing` at path > `movedMovie` by hash > create new DRAFT
- `parseMovieName(fileName, parentFolder)` → title, year, releaseType
- Tracks: `syncMovieTracksFromProbe` (`movie-tracks.ts` + `apply-probe.ts`)
- Cover: `maybeExtractCover` — non-fatal

## ffprobe.ts — медиа-анализ

- `probeMediaFile(path, signal?)` → duration, video, audio[], subtitles[]
- Parses ffprobe JSON; HDR detection (HDR10, DV, HLG); resolution labels via `resolution.ts`
- Audio: `channels.ts` — normalizeCodec, channelsToLayout, detectAudioProfile, detectTranslationType

## name-parser.ts

Strips release group tags, quality, codecs from filename. Extracts year, releaseType (bluray, web-dl, …). Falls back to parent folder name for title.

## movie-query.ts — фильтрация каталога

- `parseListQuery` → zod
- `buildMovieWhere` — status tabs, genre, resolution, hdr, audio scope/channels/format/translation, watched range, rating, duration, premium audio
- `buildMovieOrder` — title, year, rating, duration, watchedAt, createdAt
- Audio scope: `audio-track-scope.ts` + `russian-audio-formats.ts`

## catalog-facets.ts

Counts for filter chips, scoped by active status tab. Cached on home page.

## cover-storage.ts + mkv.ts

- Covers dir: `dataPath("covers")` → `./data/covers/`
- `saveCoverBuffer(movieId, buffer, ext)` — assert ext via `cover-formats-mkv.ts`
- `extractFirstMkvAttachment` — mkvextract for embedded posters
- Franchise covers: separate naming `franchise-<id>.<ext>` in franchise cover route

## cover-url.ts / franchise-cover-url.ts

Build API URLs with `?v=updatedAt.getTime()` for cache busting. Never link directly to filesystem paths.

## Slugs

- `slug.ts` — base transliteration
- `movie-slug.ts` / `franchise-slug.ts` — `resolveMovieSlug`, `resolveFranchiseSlug` with numeric suffix dedup

## Franchises

- `franchise-slots.ts` — `syncFranchiseSlots` (full replace)
- `franchise-slot-placement.ts` — story order helpers
- `franchise-metrics.ts` — 4K/HDR/Atmos/DTS-HD MA counts across filled slots
- `franchise-summary.ts`, `franchise-query.ts` — list queries
- `movie-franchise-memberships.ts` — attach/detach movie to slot

## alternative-quality.ts / movie-merge.ts

- `findDuplicateMovies` — merge candidates by `matchKey` (not title+year heuristic)
- `findAllDuplicateGroups` — for `/duplicates` page
- `releaseTabLabel` — tab label for a release (was alternative-quality cross-links)
- `mergeMovies` / `planMerge` — manual merge transaction (variant C)

## archive-metrics.ts

Total/catalog/draft/excluded counts + aggregate stats for dashboard.

## display-path.ts

Human-readable file paths (truncate home dir, storage name prefix).

## load-movie-file-meta.ts

`readMovieFileMeta`, `assertMovieFileReadable` — stat + hash for manual file path entry.

## build-movie-payload.ts

Assembles PATCH payload from form state (used by edit flows).

## Prisma client

`lib/prisma.ts` — BetterSqlite3 adapter, DATABASE_URL default `file:./data/catalog.db`. Import from `@/lib/prisma`, types from `@/generated/prisma/client`.

## Тесты рядом

`*.test.ts` для: name-parser, movie-query, slug, ffprobe helpers, catalog-facets, channels, cover-url, franchise-slug, …

При изменении логики — обновлять или добавлять тест, если поведение нетривиальное.
